                    <div class="description body" data-button-class="caption">
                        <p>Reasons to quit smoking, materials and more are presented here. The tutorial explains that not smoking will help you live longer and let you have a little more cash on hand. The materials required to stop smoking, as told in the video, are a desire to quit, paper and pen, gum and lollipops, willpower and a calendar. Each step is highlighted, with audio explanations as well as visuals added to ensure the viewer's understanding. </p>
