                    <div class="description body" data-button-class="caption">
                        <p>This clip comes from a documentary TV series called "We Love Cigarettes," which was produced by the BBC channel. Here, a man named Alan Carr is interviewed. Carr describes himself as an ex-heavy smoker, claiming that he used to have a cigarette first thing in the morning every day before even getting dressed. However, he no longer smokes. </p>
